The '''Northern Province''' was a region of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Zeltros/Legends|Zeltros]]. In [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]] it was ruled by [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Vertag]]. At some other point, it was ruled by Governor [[Heigren]].

